title: OpenVPN over Proxy

description.text: This script will let you set up your own VPN server HTTP proxy so you can bypass DPIs in no more than a minute, even if you haven't used OpenVPN or HTTP proxies before

bulletPoints: OpenVPN over Proxy road warrior installer for Ubuntu
This installer has helped many people in countries with strict censorship
Let's you setup your own vpn server in matters of minutes
Wraps OpenVPN over proxy even if you don't have a separate proxy server
